text: Frantz Dorsainvil (born 2 July 1991) is a Haitian swimmer. He received a universality spot to compete in 50m freestyle at the 2015 Pan American Games in Toronto and finished 22nd with a time of 33.83 seconds. He competed in the men's 50 metre freestyle event at the 2016 Summer Olympics, where he ranked 83rd with a time of 30.86 seconds.
